Christine McGuinness, 34, looked sensational as she shared a selection of holiday photos with her 656,000 Instagram followers. The model, who is married to Paddy McGuinness, 48, enjoyed her first trip away in three years and travelled to Croatia with her friends.The mum-of-three sported a selection of skimpy bikinis as she relaxed by the pool.As the trip came to an end yesterday, Christine said she had an amazing time and wrote: “I followed my heart and it led me to Croatia. “Memories for life, I’m feeling very lucky, so blessed. I’ve laughed sooo much, relaxed and switched off like never before!“I definitely won’t be leaving it another three years before I catch my next flight.”While Christine was away, Paddy was at home looking after their children: Penelope and Leo, eight, and six-year-old Felicity.